=== REMAPS ===

vnoremap S( c()<Esc>P
vnoremap S{ c{}<Esc>P
vnoremap S[ c[]<Esc>P

" Centers the screen after paging down/up
nnoremap <C-d> <C-d>zz
nnoremap <C-u> <C-u>zz

" Window/Views navigation remaps
nnoremap <space>ee :vsc View.SolutionExplorer<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vc :vsc View.GitHub.Copilot.Chat<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vg :vsc View.GitWindow<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vr :vsc View.GitRepositoryWindow<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vo :vsc View.Output<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vt :vsc View.Terminal<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vx :vsc View.Toolbox<Enter>

" Editor Management
nnoremap <leader>ww :w<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>wa :vsc File.SaveAll<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>wq :wq<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>qq :vsc Window.CloseDocumentWindow<Enter>

" Buffer Management
nnoremap <leader>bn :vsc Window.NextTab<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>bp :vsc Window.PreviousTab<Enter>

" Window Navigation
nnoremap <leader>wv :vsc Window.NewVerticalTabGroup<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>wh :vsc Window.PreviousSplitPane<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>wl :vsc Window.NextSplitPane<Enter>

" Refactoring and Formatting
nnoremap <leader>rn :vsc Refactor.Rename<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>ca :vsc View.QuickActionsForPosition<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>rf :vsc Edit.FormatDocument<Enter>

" Error list remaps
nnoremap <space>tt :vsc View.ErrorList<Enter>
nnoremap <space>en :vsc View.NextError<Enter>
nnoremap <space>ep :vsc View.PreviousError<Enter>

" Search
nnoremap <leader>fg :vsc Edit.FindinFiles<Enter>
nnoremap <leader>ff :vsc Edit.GoToAll<Enter>

" Quick actions remaps
nnoremap <space>. :vsc View.QuickActionsForPosition<Enter>

=== SETTINGS ===

" Allow copy and pasting from regular clipboard
set clipboard=unnamed

set number

" Relative numbering of lines
set relativenumber

" Do not let cursor scroll below or above N number of lines when scrolling.
set scrolloff=10

" Use highlighting when doing a search.
set hlsearch

" Set the commands to save in history default number is 20.
set history=1000

